\v 7 Ngakho khangela,\x + 16.14,15; 23.8.\x* insuku ziyeza,\x + 9.25; 23.7.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, lapho abangasayikuthi: Kuphila kweN\nd kosi\nd*, eyabakhuphula abantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni leGibhithe.
